snippet.title: Cookie Cutter - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Get your first look at Cookie Cutter, an extraordinarily stylish side-scrolling Metroidvania game where you play as Cherry, a sentient robot whose creator has been kidnapped and you have to get her back - by any and all violent means necessary. Rogue Games will publish Cookie Cutter for PC in 2023.

#IGN #Gaming
